This template formats links to the [http://www.iucnredlist.org IUCN Red List] website. 

'''Usage:''' <tt><nowiki>{{IUCNlink|<id number>|<title>}}</nowiki></tt> where: 

*<id number> is the internal redlist identification number.  For example, in http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/12345/0, the id number is 12345.
*<title> is an optional parameter for that causes the link to display like [http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/12345/0 ''title''] instead of http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/12345/0.

An optional <code>rangemap=yes</code> parameter may to added to link directly to the range map rather than the general information page for a given species.